To Use the Demo Script

Install All Dependencies
    Run yarn install

Configure the Transaction Settings in /src/index.ts
    Edit the following parameters:

    const DESTINATION_WALLET = '';
    const TOKEN_AMOUNT = '1.05';
    const TOKEN_NAME = 'USDC';
    const NETWORK_NAME = 'MUMBAI'; // Options: MATIC or MUMBAI
    const MNEMONIC = 'REPLACE WITH YOUR 12 WORDS';
    const WALLET_ACCOUNT_ID = 0;

If Testing on MUMBAI Network
    Claim some free Matic at https://mumbaifaucet.com/.
    Claim some free USDC at https://faucet.circle.com.

Build the Project
    Run yarn build

To Run the Script
    Run yarn start